On August 26, 2022, the President signed into law the "Ensuring the Best Schools for Veterans Act of 2022" (S. 4458). This legislation aims to enhance the way the Department of Veterans Affairs (VA) determines and assesses education programs for compliance with the 85/15 rule. The act recognizes the efforts of Senators Tester, Moran, Collins, and Blackburn, as well as Representatives Takano and Bost, for their leadership in advancing this legislation.